data.name: list_proxies.ToolTip
data.value: List of proxy servers that must be in the [IP]:[Port] format. Also if you load these from a text file, the application will periodically check for changes in the given text file and update it's list while running. This gives you time to keep scraping to the same text file while the application is running.

data.name: button_loadproxies.ToolTip
data.value: Load a list of proxies in the [IP]:[Port] format. The application will periodically check for changes in the given text file and update it's list while running. This gives you time to keep scraping to the same text file while the application is running.

data.name: button_getcoords.ToolTip
data.value: After clicking this you have 5 seconds to move your cursor to where you would like to click on every iteration. In order for the auto click to work, you must scroll the div element into view by setting either an elements ID or class name using the textbox and dropdown above. Then while the element is in view on the browser below, click set then put your cursor where you'd like it to click. Once you see the coordinate appear in the text box your good to go.
